A.R.8.3.1:M4_M1 { @ Risk_Floating_net space to Mn (from M1 to Mtop) [connects to OD] < 0.23 um, >= 0.17 um is not allowed Definition: 1. Risk_Floating_net: cumulative floating metal and VIA top area [cumulative area > 1.20E+06 um2, from M1 to top metal and VIA1 to top VIA, and doesn't connect to OD] 2. floating metal and VIA: metal and VIA doesn't connect to OD This rule is checked by the cumulative connections (from M1 to top metal and VIA1 to top VIA respectively)   
