A.R.8.3.2:M4_M1 { @ Risk_Floating_net space to Mn (from M1 to Mtop) [connects to OD] < 0.5 um, >= 0.23 um is not allowed Definition: 1. Risk_Floating_net: cumulative floating metal and VIA top area [cumulative area > 2.20E+06 um2, from M1 to top metal and VIA1 to top VIA, and doesn't connect to OD] 2. floating metal and VIA: metal and VIA doesn't connect to OD This rule is checked by the cumulative connections (from M1 to top metal and VIA1 to top VIA respectively)   
   M1_wi_DIO = NET AREA RATIO M1 SD > 0 [!!AREA(SD)]
   M1_CHK1 = M1 INTERACT (NET AREA RATIO M4 VIA3 SD IMD_M1_M1_A > A_R_8_3_2_A ACCUMULATE ACC_M3_M1_A [!AREA(SD)*(AREA(M4)+AREA(VIA3))])
   M1_CHK3 = NET AREA RATIO M1_CHK1 M4 > 0

